Requirements
-----------------------------------------------

Documentation
-----------------------------------------------
This module allows you to add multilanguage fields to your page/dataobjects.


Installation Instructions
-----------------------------------------------
1. Place this module in your root of your Silverstripe installation. 
2. Run yoursitename.com/dev/build/?flush=1. 
3. Change your settings like langs and exclude words as you prefer in multilanguage/_config.php. 

Usage Overview
-----------------------------------------------
Use this module if you want to add multilanguage to your site in
an easy way.
